{"tid":1332090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大波Man、李私煙、周融啲撚屌都開始出場，你地班友仲咁得閒屌飯民，針對五大訴求啦！","createTime":"2019-07-19T07:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:07:29.000Z","uid":34677,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7b17e01d3927e4663e70b29c008b47bdf54f90f3","tid":1332090,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"你地係咪想又好似2014咁互屌屌到完場 <br />\n最後又無事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢班垃圾又開始進場 代表的on9野又會好似2014咁再出現<br />\n點解會咁？因為2014 work 今日咪再做一次囉<br />\n你地班友而家淨係掛住屌飯民 屌分化 同2014病咩分別<br />\n要屌點都屌左呢班小丑先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要係著眼返五大訴求啦</span></strong><br />\n記住同一陣線唔代表意見完全一致<br />\n而家係到互屌完全違背哂乜鳩各自爬山<br />\n總之一句 槍口係對外 唔係而家走黎清算"},{"pid":"13216e00dbcd70ffb9874ed1c723b4b4fac62a9b","tid":1332090,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b393efaaffb46946ebeaa40616487adfacbc57","tid":1332090,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a45b254ab5a6b34d1b621ab5bcefc8ff7ef9861","tid":1332090,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"有時見到真係唔屌唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日屌飯民 屌你老母 佢地點講都企係呢邊<br />\n件事解決左再處理都唔遲<br />\n<br />\n我都好撚憎的飯民<br />\n但用下個腦啦 而家對手係邊個"},{"pid":"d6812651743b7a02aa1613a354b4ccec15fdc81a","tid":1332090,"uid":186294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隨街帶紅色Marker、白紙、膠紙，將建制720遊行改做721</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgm